!! THIS VERSION OF CCMATH SHOULD ONLY BE USED FOR RAVL !!
---------------------------------------------------------

This is NOT an offical or complete release of ccmath, there are 
many minor tweeks to get his code to compile with c++ on various 
platforms, and to make it work with the QMake make system. 

The current version was retrieved from 

  http://freshmeat.net/projects/ccmath


